>苑要拆樓<br />\n兩登好多後生未必知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%93%E6%B4%B2%E8%A7%92%E7%9F%AD%E6%A8%81%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259C%2593%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%259F%25AD%25E6%25A8%2581%25E6%25A1%2588&d=fhdlPiFVFXeDFHzej5WIfS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4d1d62d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%93%E6%B4%B2%E8%A7%92%E7%9F%AD%E6%A8%81%E6%A1%88</a><br />\n<br />\n愉翠苑（英文：Yu Chui Court，在計劃興建時稱圓翠苑）是香港房屋署轄下一個居者有其屋計劃屋苑，位於新界沙田圓洲角，為香港居屋短樁醜聞的主角之一，因而廣為香港人所認識。而D及E座亦因此事件而需要拆卸。"},{"pid":"60bcf776b0b6ad0c8f18f0d6b4054e59c29773bc","tid":856590,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8851f61c35bd1c49c1f132b1e47ff6573cd5c04d","tid":856590,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T21:12:58.000Z","msg":"高鐵開始已經無哂 discipline <br />\nW線九巴好肯定唔係喺度正常營商嘅<br />\n再數前啲，仲有八萬五時代嘅短樁樓，最後搞到愉田苑要拆樓<br />\n兩登好多後生未必知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T21:18:56.000Z","msg":"高鐵開始已經無哂 discipline<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f98cecb012d17d1ece237c12802431b34daefbc","tid":856590,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}